  4.<em> &quot;Daily News&quot;</em>, 7th August 1861 and <em>&quot;Bradford Observer&quot;</em>, 15th August 1861<br>
  5.<em> &quot;Wakefield Express&quot;</em>, 21st February 1876<br>
