  9. <em>&quot;Ossett Observer&quot;</em>, 2nd October 1880<br>
  10. <em>&quot;Gartside Manuscripts&quot;</em>, John Goodchild Collection, Wakefield<br>
  11.<em> &quot;Ossett Observer&quot;</em>, 13th December 1890<br>
  12.<em> &quot;Ossett Observer&quot;</em>, 12th December 1891<br>
