2.<em> &quot;Morning Chronicle&quot;</em>, 14th September 1859<br>
3.<em> &quot;Huddersfield Chronicle&quot;</em>, 21st June 1862<br>
4.<em> &quot;Huddersfield Chronicle&quot;</em>, 14th October 1862<br>
5.<em> &quot;Leeds Mercury&quot;</em>, 14th March 1863<br>
6. <em>&quot;Leeds Mercury&quot;</em>, 27th February 1864<br>
7.<em> &quot;Ossett Observer&quot;</em>, 4th January 1890<br>
